text:
The class header javadoc for the Level class (http://logging.apache.org/log4j/1.2/apidocs/org/apache/log4j/Level.html) is missing a comma between INFO and DEBUG. 

"Defines the minimum set of levels recognized by the system, that is OFF, FATAL, ERROR, WARN, INFODEBUG and ALL." should be "Defines the minimum set of levels recognized by the system, that is OFF, FATAL, ERROR, WARN, INFO, DEBUG and ALL."
creator: gthomas.cs02@gtalumni.org
gcasf@redtown.org

All that is missing is a '>' and 'INFO<code'. I added a patch with the relevant change.
